Text.val: First Get Instrument Quotes and Update InstrumentDetails
Recalculate dynamic and sub models for which all clac proportions for the details are updated
and update details which have this model as a submodeldetail.

SQL_STMT_U.val: select m.id, sum(d.dyna_calc_proportion), m.dynamic_ind from model_details d inner join models m on m.id = d.model_id where (m.submodel_ind = 1 or m.dynamic_ind = 1) and not exists ( select 1 from model_details d1 where d1.model_id = m.id and d1.dyna_calc_proportion is null) group by m.id, m.dynamic_ind

Text.val: Update all model_details using this model as a submodel
Only update proportions for dynamic models
